               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17491011-43-off189-c185" targOrder="Y" targets="t17491011-43-defend265 t17491011-43-off189 t17491011-43-verdict191"></join>
         
               <p>451. 
               
                  <persName id="t17491011-43-defend265" type="defendantName">
                     Francis 
                     Forbes 
                  <interp inst="t17491011-43-defend265" type="surname" value="Forbes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-defend265" type="given" value="Francis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-defend265" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17491011-43-off189" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-off189" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-off189" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="174910110012"></xptr> one pair of cloth breeches, val 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17491011-43-victim266" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Gavin 
               <interp inst="t17491011-43-victim266" type="surname" value="Gavin"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-victim266" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-victim266" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17491011-43-off189 t17491011-43-victim266"></join>
                  </persName>
              
                  <rs id="t17491011-43-cd190" type="crimeDate">Sept. 12</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17491011-43-off189 t17491011-43-cd190"></join>.</p>
               <p>The prisoner went to buy a pair of breeches at the Mr. Gavin was turning himself me down to shew him, the prisoner his coat; the prosecutor took of the shop with them upon him; and him found he had no money about him to buy.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17491011-43-verdict191" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-verdict191" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs> Felony.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17491011-43-punish192" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17491011-43-punish192" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17491011-43-defend265 t17491011-43-punish192"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
